import React from 'react' import { useState, useEffect } from 'react' import freeUserPic from '../assets/user_profilepic.jpeg' import UserMenu from './UserMenu' function UserHomepage({currentUser, setCurrentUser, newUser, setNewUser}) { const [userData, setUserData] = useState([]) useEffect(() => { fetch('/user-homepage') .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { setUserData(data) }) }, []) return (

{userData.name} Homepage

Welcome, {userData.name}

{userData.username}

Location: {userData.location}

Contact: {userData.email}

Camera Equipment: {userData.camera}

Editing Software: {userData.editing}

Light Kit: {userData.lights}

Audio Equipment: {userData.audio}

Props: {userData.props}

Bio: {userData.bio}

) } export default UserHomepage
